snippet.title: The 2017 Brazil Prison Riots | We're Going to Brazil
snippet.description:
Brazil is already scary, and known for many things but on my channel it's the brutal gore videos that come from the beautiful nation. In 2017 riots broke out in up to four Brazilian Prisons and the most discussed one had some of the most brutal violence seen since the 1992 Massacre of Carindiru. 

Wild as hell, we'll talk about that and a bit of what else is to come! (Albert Fish is coming too don't worry)
